glosses.gloss: The gymnastic moves of an acrobat
Acrobatics is the performance of extraordinary human feats of balance, agility, and motor coordination.
Aerial silk, aerial hoop, rope or corde lisse.
The art of performing acrobatic gymnastic feats.
곡예는 무대 예술 및 스포츠 경기로 진행되는 신체 운동이다.
The performance of stunts while in flight in an aircraft
In radio broadcasting, stunting occurs when a station abruptly airs content that is seemingly uncharacteristic compared to what they normally play.
Aerobatics is the practice of flying maneuvers involving aircraft attitudes that are not used in normal flight.
When a radio station abruptly begins broadcasting seemingly uncharacteristic programming
The practice of flying maneuvers involving aircraft
Flying maneuvers involving attitudes not attained during normal flight
